      "content": "that's a hard thing to hear, but it feels so true. i just feel like a weight around their necks. sometimes i wonder if they'd actually be able to focus on their own lives and their own kids if they didn't have to constantly worry about me. like, if they didn't have to deal with my appointments and my mess... would they be happier?",
